<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>鬼滅の刃 on 元视角</title><link>https://blog.yuanpei.me/tags/%E9%AC%BC%E6%BB%85%E3%81%AE%E5%88%83/</link><description>Recent content in 鬼滅の刃 on 元视角</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 08 Feb 2025 07:25:23 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.yuanpei.me/tags/%E9%AC%BC%E6%BB%85%E3%81%AE%E5%88%83/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>作为技术宅的我，是这样追鬼滅の刃的</title><link>https://blog.yuanpei.me/posts/3602353334/</link><pubDate>Tue, 15 Dec 2020 22:49:47 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.yuanpei.me/posts/3602353334/</guid><description>有人说，“男人至死都是少年”，而这句听起来有一点中二的话，其实是出自一部同样有一点中二的动漫——银魂。我个人的理解是，知世故而不世故。也许，年轻时那些天马行空的想法，就像堂吉诃德大战风车一样荒诞，可依然愿意去怀着这样的梦想去生活。正如罗曼罗</description></item></channel></rss>